Hello,
 
I am also able to run the app with given code without any error when I fix the label id. [Screenshot|https://i.imgsafe.org/89ac696.png]

*index.xml:*
{code}
<Alloy>
	<Window class="container">
		<Label id="label" onClick="doClick">Hello, World</Label>
		<Label id="textoLbl"></Label>
	</Window>
</Alloy>
{code}
*index.js:*
{code}
function doClick(e) {
    alert($.label.text);
}

$.textoLbl.html = "<p>El presente curso re&uacute;ne tanto aspecto de gesti&oacute;n</br>del desempe&ntilde;o del trabajo como aspectos de gesti&oacute;n</p>";

$.index.open();
{code}

Thanks
